data.title: Arbor Snowboards :: Buffmoose is PRO
data.tags: Brandon Hammid,Buffmoose,Buffmoose is Pro,Pro Announcement,Arbor,Arbor Snowboards,Snowboarding,SLC,Think Thank
data.description: Arbor Snowboards is proud to welcome Brandon Hammid, a.k.a Buffmoose, to the pro team. After years of destroying the Salt Lake City streets and recently receiving a Transworld Rider's Poll nomination for his ender part in Think Thank is Braindead and Having a Heart Attack, Hammid has consistently proven that he's one of the best in the game. At this point, I think we all agree...Buffmoose is pro.

data.title: Arbor Snowboards :: Curtis Woodman - Full Part
data.tags: Arbor,Arbor Snowboards,Curtis Woodman,Full Part,Surf the Earth,Element,Abacus,Surfing,Snowboarding
data.description:
Curtis Woodman is an individual to the fullest extent. It’s difficult to define Curtis as both his snowboarding and personality fall outside of any societal preconceptions or stereotypes. He picks his own line down the mountain and hides in the white room most of the winter. We’ve been lucky enough to get a glimpse into the mind of Curtis through his Surf The Earth video series over the past few months. And now, without further ado, Curtis presents the culmination of all his hard work from last season in his Surf The Earth – Full Part.

data.title: Arbor Snowboards :: Steve Klassen x The Steepwater
data.tags: Arbor,Arbor Snowboards,Steve Klassen,Steepwater,Snowboarding,Big Mountain,Verbier,Freeride Tour,Wave Rave,Big Mountain Snowboarding,Freeriding
data.description: The Steepwater, a big mountain “rocket” built for high speed stability in variable terrain, was actualized through a collaboration between Arbor Snowboards and Steve Klassen, owner of Wave Rave snowboard shop in Mammoth, CA and 5x winner of the Verbier Extreme. Steve’s nearly 20 years of R&D experience has allowed us to create a premium, one-of-a-kind snowboard designed with the big mountain enthusiast in mind. This is the story of the Steepwater.

data.title: Arbor Skateboards :: Jasper Ohlson x The Backlash 37
data.tags: Arbor,Arbor Skateboards,Skateboarding,Jasper Ohlson,Backlash 37,Downhill,Kids,Jack Boston,Wrongboarding
data.description:
Living in San Diego California, our team rider Jasper has been turning heads with his young talent. Although only 13 and continuing to hone in his skills, it is undeniable that he is on track to become one of the best freeriders in the scene.

Watch him show how the Backlash 37 is a perfect board for smaller riders who want to progress fast. From stand up slides to sidewalk slashes to bombing hills this board can do it all.

Enjoy the video, and see how this young gun is coming up!

data.title: Arbor Skateboards :: Ed Garner - Raw Run
data.tags: Arbor,Arbor Skateboards,Ed Garner,Raw Run,Skateboarding,Skating,Downhill,Downhill Skateboarding,Green Hills,Mountain Road
data.description:
East Coast team rider Ed Garner recently flew out to California to shoot for his new edit. We felt the footage was so good that it was necessary to share a pure Raw Run before the edit release. Watch Ed navigate all the pavement changes on this gnarly road in the hills of Central California, and stay tuned for the new edit coming out next week!
Team Rider: Ed Garner
Follow Cam: Tom Flinchbaugh
Edit: Nate Shute
